		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="407" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">Presuming you land without incident (although with so many flights taking off and landing at some airports, you'll wonder why far more [9] aren't reported) you could now, due to the late arrival of your plane, have missed your connection and end up spending the night at the airport waiting for the next available flight. </FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
